:"60e7425c49f13159dbb9543e1505d2650222dc3b","tid":1633107,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:38:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/goldwaterhk/videos/2772732759459253/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgoldwaterhk%2Fvideos%2F2772732759459253%2F&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4n%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=d16c4981\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/goldwaterhk/videos/2772732759459253/</a><br />\n<br />\n打車無用<br />\n一定要拉佢落車<br />\n一定要搶車匙"},{"pid":"40bf1e78348828a989bfaaf26a58b4276a62445b","tid":1633107,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:01:55.000Z","msg":"問題係手足唔夠武勇拉個司機落車"},{"pid":"3f28b1d1a1b9e02829a4ae1f61bff663904610aa","tid":1633107,"uid":35246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"講少少前傳<br />\n發夢見到<br />\n成班手足當時係哥和老街轉入石硤尾南昌街落深水埗<br />\n架的士係遠處已經癲撚左向前衝<br />\n車速好快<br />\n冇可能stop到佢 不過當時好彩冇人受傷<br />\n估唔到最後攪到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cee8ed5c6f2d07e1208b383d46a55fad35389e","tid":1633107,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:35:40.000Z","msg":"車係致命武器。<br />\n<br />\n係咪咁難明？"},{"pid":"fcab154d98644fe9e473402cda3bb4bb24161460","tid":1633107,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"你斬撚咗自己對腳再講"},{"pid":"2a0bc83a933b6c309906d60dbbc8b4f144234b52","tid":1633107,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:41:21.000Z","msg":"點解可以成件事調返轉黎講?<br />\n你講到係因為有手足打佢架車，先導致佢撞人，而忽略左佢主動移路障所以先俾人拆車既主因<br />\n我明白大家都唔想見到慘劇發生<br />\n但你有冇諗過 為咗他人安全，俾返小小空間佢，等佢和平離開。<br />\n其實係縱容緊的士狗主動衝路障?<br />\nset 路障原因就係想阻止有車衝入人群，而佢衝散路障本身已經係危險人物"}]}